channel.title: Fallenx, Web-Based Runescape Client (Just Released It's 3 month old project!)
channel.description:
[SIZE=3]NOTICE Fallen x is Web-Based that means there is NO downloads, therefor you CANT get a keylogger from it.[/SIZE]
Fallen x Runescape Client has just released its 3 month old project!
Some Features, pictures below.
All Worlds High/Low Detail Highscores IRC Chat Built in IRC Settings/Accounts Skill Calculators Combat Calculator Pest Control Calculator Updated Constantly
Here is some screen shots of Fallen x,
World list, The colors are in meaning from lowest to highest players on the world green meaning lowest yellow meaning around 1,000ish the different shades change with more players purple meaning the world is off line. [IMG]http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d18/mrgreens/Fallenxworld.jpg[/img]
Fallen x Highscores, when your registered it automatically compares you to other players as above green means your higher and more to the red they are higher yellow means your the same level. They are even designed to find the player searched CLAN and RANK. [IMG]http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d18/mrgreens/Fallenxhighscoers.jpg[/img]
Fallen x IRC, unlike some other online clients, fallen x IRC is not bulky and in the way and you don't have to scroll up and down to read whats being said. [IMG]http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d18/mrgreens/Fallenxirc.jpg[/img]
Fallen x Calculators, Created by blackarchron these are the state of the art calculators fit for your every needs if its prayer exp or agility exp it will tell you how much and how many trips you need bones to bury logs to fletch and more! [IMG]http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d18/mrgreens/Fallenxcalc.jpg[/img]
Fallen x Special Calculators, These include pest control, cannons, which give you the needed costs, combat calculator and more! [IMG]http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d18/mrgreens/FallenxScalc.jpg[/img]
Example of the PC calculator. [IMG]http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d18/mrgreens/Fallenxpc.jpg[/img]
Fallen x Tabs, These are designed so you don't have to open a new window every time you click highscores or irc chat you get a new tab that you can close at any time and not disrupt your game play! [IMG]http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d18/mrgreens/FallenxTabs.jpg[/img]
Fallen x Reminder, this remarkable tool is great for when you play runescape if you're playing before work and you're late this timer will buzz and save you a hard time at work or even your favorite T.V. show is coming on you just set the date and time select your sound that you would like to hear and at the exact minute of your selection it will go off; it's truly amazing! [IMG]http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d18/mrgreens/Fallenxreminder.jpg[/img]
Fallen x Overview, This is the playing screen view of fallenx, its minimized to load faster for you guys =) [IMG]http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d18/mrgreens/FallenxFullView.jpg[/img]
This client is completely Web-Based there is NO downloads that you have to get, so its automatic updates.
The client can be found at [URL=http://www.fallenx.com]Fallenx[/URL]
Or
www.fallenx.com
IF YOU TRY IT PLEASE LEAVE FEEDBACk.
